reference.title: AArch32 PMU register summary
reference.shortdesc: The PMU counters and their associated control registers are accessible in the AArch32 Execution state from the internal CP15 system register interface with MCR and MRC instructions for 32-bit registers and MCRR and MRRC for 64-bit registers.
